IRS990.MissionDesc: TO SUSTAIN A SYMPHONY ORCHESTRA IN SAN ANGELO; TO PROMOTE THE HIGHEST CALIBER MUSIC PROGRAMMING WITH AN EMPHASIS ON SYMPHONIC MUSIC FOR THE ENJOYMENT AND ENRICHMENT OF OUR AUDIENCES; AND TO ENHANCE DIVERSE MUSIC EDUCATION IN THE CONCHO VALLEY.
